Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.99,Japanese Calligraphy,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Calligraphy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.46,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Calligraphy."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.24,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Love and Courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.70,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:43.08,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Write your favorite word and\N submit it by the end of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:43.08,Black Signs,Paper(L),0000,0250,0050,,Effort
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:43.08,Black Signs,Paper(L),0300,0000,0050,,Love and\NCourage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.16,Main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Favorite word?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.55,Main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna write?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.75,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Having trouble deciding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:56.22,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided what you're gonna write, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.14,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:04.18,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Why don't we write\N what we want from each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.48,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What we want... from each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.22,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.17,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.21,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What I want from Такаги-сан...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.41,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1150,1)}Teasing Prohibited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.06,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.79,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A message telling her not to tease me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.09,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... That might backfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.83,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан would probably enjoy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:41.27,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A word that'll make Такаги-сан\N remorseful without provoking her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.65,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.52,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You done, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.74,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.12,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we show each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.28,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Status Quo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.99,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.29,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.60,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,"Restraint"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.70,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:10.46,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Of what? It's something\N you want from me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.60,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... On various things...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:16.48,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:21.08,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,But if she did get it, it'd\N have an adverse effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.09,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,This is tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:29.26,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about you?\N What do you mean by "status quo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.58,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:38.03,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I want Нисиката to stay\N the way he is. Easy to tease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.36,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, Такаги-сан is going on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.46,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how she wants to play this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.33,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.95,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.37,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.98,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.26,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on the offensive this time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.54,Main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.13,Main,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.35,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:15.35,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I'll make Такаги-сан \N realize she isn't very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.32,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this will upset you, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.57,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What should I write...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:25.06,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You look uncertain, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:29.79,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's all due to\N your lack of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:34.50,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, your handwriting is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.15,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It looks interesting. Did you\N learn calligraphy somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.50,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.30,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like your handwriting, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.40,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.08,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.95,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's nice all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.91,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.58,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? Is Такаги-сан actually pretty nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.18,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,but I just haven't noticed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.25,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.24,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.97,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката, stay still for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.24,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.81,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You had something on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.15,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I thought of a good word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.22,Run,Paper(R),0000,0080,0050,,Running
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.45,Black Signs,Paper(R),0000,0000,0250,,Grilled Meat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.45,Winning lawsuit,Paper(R),0000,0000,0000,,Winning Lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:05:59.58,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.32,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Show me yours first, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.71,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Not at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.36,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Just show me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.72,Black Signs,Papaer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.82,Italics,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I rewrote it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:17.79,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have interesting handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.98,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! {\i1}That's{\i0} your comment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.33,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I want you to stop teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.43,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.82,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:31.16,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right. I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.79,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.17,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.69,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.34,Black Signs,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,You have ink on your cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.06,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You did it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:02.27,Main,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You just said you'd try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.98,Main,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,But I did it before I said that.
